sentences: Rodek was born in 1977 in Brzeg, Poland.
Rodek studied conducting from 1998 to 2003 at the Music Academy in Wroclaw, Poland.
In 2005 he won the competition for the position of Assistant Conductor of the National Philharmonic Orchestra in Warsaw.
In December, 2011, Wojciech Rodek was appointed artistic director of the Lublin Philharmonic.
